General observations: Old-growth northern coniferous forest. Tree to four creted tits seem upset after recordist mimicks the autumn call of the Eurasian Pygmy Owl Glaucidium passerinum

  • Eurasian Treecreeper, Certhia familiaris, call, srree srree srree, at 0:25
  • Great Spotted Woodpecker Dendrocopos major, foraging, at e.g. 0:22
